{"tid":2182464,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"藏白電油打火機雷射筆 17歲男生判勞教中心","createTime":"2020-08-31T10:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T10:58:00.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"37bd79d4b74df73c1bf5836afdd4ad5cd235dd1e","tid":2182464,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T10:08:08.000Z","msg":"警方於去年11月「曙光行動」當天到中環驅散示威者，其間拘捕17歲男生，指他躱避警方時，將裝有白電油、打火機及雷射筆等物品的背囊丟到路上。男生早前於東區裁判法院承認在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪，求情曾指因為對政府感失望，及對未來絕望才犯案。主任裁判官錢禮今判刑，接受報告建議，判被告入勞教中心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200831/OJQBLU3BJ5FPZKK42JIBIECRLQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200831%2FOJQBLU3BJ5FPZKK42JIBIECRLQ%2F&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr0wX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=70613bd7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200831%2FOJQBLU3BJ5FPZKK42JIBIECRLQ%2F&h=d390ff34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200831/OJQBLU3BJ5FPZKK42JIBIECRLQ/</a>"},{"pid":"8eaa90e393e75465ad56d3fe26a2b86e54cddd81","tid":2182464,"uid":67237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T10:10:13.000Z","msg":"唉，無知問句，判勞教即係有冇案底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6645adf5d4d2cfb66284b322f214fad0035ac643","tid":2182464,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T10:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f71a9f4e661e6eff7f03812fbda8f4f7d2b6af7","tid":2182464,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T10:10:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"985a3febde78eb33e9027d92cac5116387e6c3b9","tid":2182464,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote